name: Oracle Dao
description: Oracle DAO's vision is to build a decentralized cross-dimensional connection between the real and virtual worlds for its community members by combining DEFI 3.0, DAO and NFT . With the mission to establish a new industrial ecosystem that can be empowered through the combination of virtual and real world, Oracle DAO will unite outstanding community talents and resources, and follow the trend of Web 3.0 to develop a true Oracle DAO community with unlimited discovery and expansion of the ecosystem
